      <hedline>
        <hl1>Can't Find a Parking Spot? Aww.</hl1>
      </hedline>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>A public service advertising campaign should be started to encourage people who live in the suburbs to use public transportation to get in and out of the city. Having fewer cars in the city would improve the quality of life and would expose suburbanites to the social benefits of not using a car.</p>
        <p>MICHAEL P. GAUGHAN  Kensington, Brooklyn</p>
      </block>
